comments: Jones (SAC) begins rolling toward the lane following the expiration of the pick and marginal contact occurs with Okogie (MIN) as Okogie goes under.
Towns (MIN) and Jones (SAC) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Jones (SAC) moves alongside Towns' (MIN) path and marginal body contact occurs during Towns' drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Hield (SAC) backs up toward Okogie (MIN) and marginal contact occurs with Okogie's front during the rebound and subsequent put-back attempt.
Okogie (MIN) and Hield (SAC) make incidental contact with one another as they each attempt to gain control of the rebound.
Towns (MIN) extends his left arm outward and marginal contact occurs with Fox's (SAC) front as he moves to contest the jump shot attempt.
Hield (SAC) and Rubio (MIN) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Hield (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in McDaniels' (MIN) path and absorbs the contact. They each engage and disengage with one another thereafter.
McDaniels (MIN) engages and disengages with Hield (SAC) during the inbound.
Rubio (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Jones' (SAC) path and absorbs the contact.
Towns (MIN) extends his right arm forward and initiates contact with Fox's left arm (SAC) during the driving shot attempt.
Jones (SAC) and Towns (MIN) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Jones (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Russell's (MIN) path and absorbs the contact.
Russell (MIN) moves forward toward Haliburton (SAC) and marginal body contact occurs as Haliburton is passing.
Rubio (MIN) has his hands on Hield's (SAC) midsection and quickly removes them as Hield moves along the perimeter.
Rubio (MIN) extends his arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Barnes' (SAC) front as he is passing.
Jones (SAC) and Towns (MIN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Rubio (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Jones' (SAC) path and absorbs the contact as he moves slightly forward.
Jones (SAC) moves alongside Towns' (MIN) path and marginal contact occurs with Towns as he is drifting away from the basket during his driving shot attempt.
McDaniels (MIN) commits a take foul on Fox (SAC).
